ctification campaign reform, in-depth and healthy will not only create the necessary conditions, and it also needs the co-ordination of reform. In concentrate during the rectification and reform should focus on the rectification and service it. Rectification is not positive, is not active on the reform. At present, we should focus on the enterprise contract responsibility system, fiscal responsibility system, financial system, foreign trade contracting system to deepen and perfect the reform. We must continue to adhere to the policy of opening up to the outside world, the active use of foreign capital and the introduction of advanced technology, more effective expansion of foreign trade and economic and technological exchanges. The same basic policy measures in the special economic zones and open coastal areas, and gradually be improved in practice. <br> plenary session discussed and adopted the \"thirteenth Fifth Plenary Session of the Communist Party of China on the decision to agree with Comrade Deng Xiaoping resigned from the CPC Central Military Commission presidency. The (Lssdjt.com) <br> plenary session, Comrade Deng Xiaoping resigned proceed from the fundamental interests of the party and the country still in good health when current positions, to achieve the long-cherished wish he repeatedly raised over the years completely stepping down from the leadership post , the performance of the broad mind of a great proletarian revolutionary. The participants all the comrades he personally express our highest respect for the abolition of leading life-long tenure made exemplary. <br> Plenary spoke highly of the remarkable feats of Comrade Deng Xiaoping, our party and the country. Comrade Deng Xiaoping is an outstanding leader of recognized prestige enjoyed by people of all ethnic groups in China, and have made a significant contribution in the various historical periods of the revolution and construction of the party leadership. Especially after the Third Plenary Se